# Shield — DDoS protection

Protects against **distributed denial-of-service** attacks. Two tiers.

## Shield Standard

- **Free**, automatic, on for **every** account
- Defends **L3 / L4** — SYN floods, UDP reflection, volumetric
- Covers CloudFront, Route 53, ELB, EC2 Elastic IPs

## Shield Advanced — $3,000 / org / month

- **L7 DDoS** — HTTP floods, slowloris (CloudFront, ALB, API GW)
- **DDoS cost protection** — credits the scaling charges an attack caused
- **24/7 Shield Response Team (SRT)** — experts during an attack
- Advanced real-time metrics + global threat dashboards

**Cues:** free / L3-L4 → **Standard**. L7, cost protection, SRT, post-attack bill → **Advanced**.
